1
00:00:05,986 --> 00:00:09,202
We’re trying to please 
Guru and Vaiṣṇava.

2
00:00:09,402 --> 00:00:12,708
[Dress for Kṛṣṇa]

3
00:00:12,862 --> 00:00:15,426
Like Avadhūt Mahārāj
was once telling,

4
00:00:15,426 --> 00:00:18,730
in the Russian circus
there’s always a bear

5
00:00:18,730 --> 00:00:24,591
who rides a bicycle, or a unicycle
or something like that

6
00:00:24,591 --> 00:00:28,480
—not that that’s the only thing,
but that’s kind of standard,

7
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:32,512
there should be a bear 
riding a bicycle.

8
00:00:32,912 --> 00:00:37,451
So Avadhūt Mahārāj said humbly
when he took sannyās,

9
00:00:37,451 --> 00:00:41,477
“If I’m like the Russian bear
riding the bicycle

10
00:00:41,477 --> 00:00:45,664
for the amusement of Gurudev, 
then that’s my happiness.”

11
00:00:45,864 --> 00:00:50,257
He was saying it humbly, 
“Is this not comical?

12
00:00:50,257 --> 00:00:53,805
But if it gives
my Gurudev happiness,

13
00:00:53,805 --> 00:00:59,198
then a laugh at my expense, 
it’s okay.”

14
00:00:59,198 --> 00:01:03,297
So who are we concerned about?

15
00:01:03,297 --> 00:01:07,046
Who are we concerned
what we look like to?

16
00:01:07,046 --> 00:01:11,966
The people of the world, 
or Guru and Vaiṣṇava?

17
00:01:11,966 --> 00:01:18,498
Gopīs decorate themselves, 
they make themselves look nice for Kṛṣṇa.

18
00:01:22,218 --> 00:01:26,871
I always have a running dialog,
“Do women make themselves look nice

19
00:01:26,871 --> 00:01:29,844
for men or for other women?”

20
00:01:29,844 --> 00:01:34,636
One week it’s for men, 
one week it’s for other women,

21
00:01:34,636 --> 00:01:37,401
and it will go on 
until the end of time,

22
00:01:37,401 --> 00:01:40,587
this all-important dialog.

23
00:01:41,877 --> 00:01:44,435
But what we’re told is,
the Vraja-gopīs,

24
00:01:44,435 --> 00:01:48,241
they make themselves 
look nice for Kṛṣṇa.

25
00:01:48,241 --> 00:01:49,604
That’s why.

26
00:01:49,604 --> 00:01:51,488
And that’s a very beautiful thing,

27
00:01:51,488 --> 00:01:53,418
so they’re dressing nicely.

